<h1 class="aboutheader">About</h1>

<div class="appdesc">
	Have you ever been bored with a spouse or group of friends not knowing what to do? then whatnow could be just for you.  It will help you decide your choice of where to go. Whatnow provides the user with an event that is based to their preferences at the time. 

	Whatnow was designed with the users experience in mind. It was made to make it as easy as possible for someone to make up their minds about where they were going to go or just to give them a suggestion. 
</div>

